Value: body{font-family:"Trebuchet MS", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;}#logTable{font-family:"Trebuchet MS", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;}#logTable td, #customers th {font-size:1.2em;border:1px solid #98bf21;padding:3px 7px 2px 7px;}#logTable th {font-size:1.4em;text-align:left;padding-top:5px;padding-bottom:4px;background-color:#A7C942;color:#fff;}#logTable tr.alt td {color:#000;background-color:#EAF2D3;}
